{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It took us about three days to get there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is a chapter by itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when we came, when the doors opened up, we literally fell out from these trains, from these cattle cars, with our bundles-- whatever we took with us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were selected-- women separately, men separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then each group was, again, selected, between those who were still capable of work went to one place, and those who were not went to a different place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were marched off directly to the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now in case of Rumkowski, when he came in, eyewitnesses told us, later on, after the liberation, that he was picked out from the trains.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He came in the same cattle train, in the same cattle car, together with-- with all others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was picked out from the train, directly, and moved straight to the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He and the family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it did not save-- no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the way he acted-- and peop-- eyewitness told us later on that, until the last minute, he still believed that he is still the head of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when he came down, when he came off the train, he behaved himself like he-- I mean, he beheld-- behaved himself like he would be still the head of a-- of a-- of the Jews or of a Jewish group, and so on.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But soon he realized, when the German-- when the Germans in Auschwitz took him over, that he's no longer what he used to be.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He is no longer the boss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I mentioned a while ago, the whole family was in this cattle car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say we were about more than about 80, 90 people packed in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no room even to stand.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
